features: NO MORE FLOPPY, WEIRLY SHAPED BASKETS: “My baskets came flat and now they won’t stand up straight!” If this sounds familiar, you may be a victim of “squashed basket syndrome.” Not on our watch! While competitors send folded baskets that droop and sag, ours are stacked together in their own gift box so they don’t get smushed during shipping. No more sad, floppy cotton rope storage baskets!

5 BASKETS FOR 5X THE ORGANIZING POWER: Life is messy...but your house doesn’t have to be! With 5 beautiful rope baskets for organizing, you’ll defeat messy rooms like a true supermom! Use the largest baskets for Montessori displays or countertop fruits holder, create the cutest dog toy storage or bathroom hand towel holder with the medium ones and stash jewelry or keys in the smallest. Biggest (11.8"x8.7"x4.3"), (11"x7.9"x3.9"), (10.2"x7.1"x3.5"), (9.1"x6.3"x3.1"), Smallest (7.9x5.5"x2.8")

MADE FROM SAFE, NATURAL COTTON: Nom, nom, nom! When you’re revamping the nursery with some seriously stylish toy basket, your little one is bound to turn basket handles into their own personal teethers. No worries, mom! Our woven baskets for storage are made from 100% natural cotton, so they’re completely safe for little mouths and hands. No toxic chemicals or ingredients! Plus, you won’t find a single faux leather anywhere that could be harmful for your little one or your pet.

DOUBLE REINFORCED & SCRATCH-FREE DESIGN: When you’re a full-time mom or dad, you need a storage solution that works just as hard as you do. With reinforced stitching on the handles and base, our woven storage basket set is ready to tackle some heavy-duty actions and will sustain the roughest toddler play. With our soft yet firm handwoven rope basket designs, you’ll never have to worry about scratches or marks being left on your coffee table, shelf, front door table, nightstand or any tabletop.

ELEGANTLY DESIGNED TO MATCH ANY DÉCOR: Classic neutral colors that match ANY design scheme? Yes, please! From boho chic to rustic farmhouse, modern and traditional design schemes, our rectangle basket makes the perfect accents to any decor. Plus, you won’t find a single tacky logo anywhere in sight!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love these baskets. Very well made and came fast and in great condition. I first bought the cream color and then I ordered the pink and also the grey. They hold a lot and the five different sizes allows me to put some on the bathroom counters and in the closet for great storage of hair products, etc. Boyfriend put his colognes in one and has it on his dresser. Looks great! Would definitely recommend. You will not be disappointed!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good value for price. Look nice and good quality.
reviews.reviewText: I love that these baskets are cotton because they feel nice and look good. They have no weird smell, which seems to be an issue with a lot of fabric things from Amazon. There are a lot of different sizes and I haven't found uses for them all yet. I use the largest one to hold skincare and haircare and it fits perfectly on my vanity. I use the other ones for medication and miscellaneous stuff. I love these for meds because the sides are the perfect height for bottles so they don't fall out, but I can still clearly see the labels especially on bigger supplement bottles. I like that stuff doesn't roll over in these because they're fabric. If I tried to store meds in a plastic bin, they'd fall over and roll around. Also they're a great value for the price. If I had bought these somewhere else like Target, I would've had to buy them individually for $10+ each.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute and Durable, but Smaller Than Expected
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased a set of these woven baskets, and while I found them to be cute and incredibly durable, I was a bit surprised by their size.Let’s start with the positives. These baskets are undeniably well-made. The quality of the weaving and the materials used is outstanding, and I have no doubt that they will last for a long time. The durability is a big plus, as they can handle daily wear and tear with ease.In terms of aesthetics, these baskets are absolutely adorable. The woven design gives them a charming, rustic feel that adds a lovely touch to any room. They’re not only functional but also decorative.However, my only gripe is that they are smaller than I had anticipated. When I ordered them, I had a particular use in mind, and I thought they would be a bit larger. So, if you’re planning to store larger items in these baskets, be prepared for a bit of a squeeze.Despite the size issue, I do find these baskets to be a worthwhile purchase due to their durability and cuteness. Just be sure to check the dimensions carefully and set your expectations accordingly. They’re perfect for smaller items or as decorative accents in your living space.
